title: Refrigerator Dairy Door - Clear
description: Refrigerator Dairy Door - Clear ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 7 Reviews PartSelect Number PS1525960 Manufacturer Part Number 240337712 This is a dairy door for your refrigerator. This part covers the products in the dairy bin section. To access this section, simply lift the lid. This dairy door is made entirely of plastic and is transparent. It is almost 10 inches wide, and roughly 6 inches long. In order to make this repair you will not need any tools, as this part will easily clip in and out of place of the hinged holes.
